(52, 1, '2019-11-21 16:27:00', '2019-11-21 16:27:00', '<div id=\"pl-7\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-7-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;quangnguyen&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;23&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment_fallback&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;cover&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"quangnguyen\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-7-0\" ><div id=\"pgc-7-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-7-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;container&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" data-label=\"Quảng Nguyên\" ><div class=\"container panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-7-0-0-0\" ><div id=\"pl-w5dd6bad426353\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-w5dd6bad426353-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-w5dd6bad426353-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-w5dd6bad426353-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Quảng Nguyên</h3><div class=\"textwidget\"><h4>Công ty cổ phần thương mại dược phẩm Quảng Nguyên</h4>\nXây dựng văn hóa kinh doanh với phương châm “ chất lượng sản phẩm tạo nên thương hiêu”. Mọi hoạt động của công ty và nhân viên đều hướng tới mục tiêu cao nhất là thỏa mãn nhu cầu sử dụng sản phẩm chất lượng