g của khách hàng. Xây dựng hệ thống nguyên tắc ứng xử, giao tiếp tối ưu đối với khách hàng. Đồng thời công ty cũng thực hiện những chương trình chăm sóc với nhiều nội dung hấp dẫn, thiết thực nhằm đảm bảo quyền lợi và gia tang lợi ích cho khách hàng,\n\n<a class=\"read_m\" href=\"https://duocquangnguyen.com/gioi-thieu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Xem thêm</a></div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-w5de9c5281dbb8-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-w5de9c5281dbb8-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"textwidget\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KQ-Ad-359gQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-7-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;product_home&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"product_home\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-7-1\" ><div id=\"pgc-7-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-7-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;container&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" data-label=\"Sản phẩm\" ><div class=\"container panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-7-1-0-0\" ><div id=\"pl-w5dd6e11906935\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-w5dd6e11906935-0\"  cl